{"tid":775232,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普：今季劍指冠軍！","createTime":"2018-08-11T04:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T04:54:19.000Z","uid":153600,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a4e942629f635245c27f0c4000c3b5744bfcace8","tid":775232,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:06:32.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Oduy08sX6Lr3Yv6xxZYNfTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=bf145945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】今夏大灑金錢擴軍後，利物浦主帥高普揚言紅軍今季目標就是挑戰英超冠軍，冀能得幸運之神眷顧達成目標。<br />\n<br />\n周日開鑼戰對韋斯咸前，利物浦領隊高普（Jurgen Klopp）談及擴軍後對紅軍的期望：「總會有花錢花得比較多的一個球季。己隊一心打造一支實力夠強、足以招架英超列強的球隊。今季己隊要抱著爭冠軍的心態來比賽，勇往直前直至耗盡所有空氣所有氧氣為止，全力以赴不勝無歸。」<br />\n<br />\n高普以電影《洛奇》裡的角色來比較曼城與紅軍：「曼城是冠軍隊，今夏沒有流失任何球員，但就買入了馬列斯，實力有增無減。我看過他們對車路士一役，表現令人留下深刻印象。己隊始終是洛奇而不是（他的對手蘇聯拳王）Ivan Drago，我們還是需要付出更多、揮拳更多的一隊，我們必須具備這種態度。」<br />\n<br />\n「己隊至今還沒有勝出過甚麼，只打入了（歐聯）決賽，假如己隊再獲得這個機會的話，就該一舉取得勝利。聯賽的情況亦然。」高普續說，「己隊需要多一點運氣。有人說己隊是黑仔王，正因如此，在重要關頭己隊必須交出更加穩定、更加進取的表現。」"},{"pid":"55113146c996e5ed8ce7c5185f090f05303f553b","tid":775232,"uid":161311,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:34:37.000Z","msg":"條柒頭知唔知依家邊個第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d985b86639c9ee7256245842cb96385a0a5e014","tid":775232,"uid":13797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:39:38.000Z","msg":"有摩三季係到<br />\n仲想拎冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c8aa7493557beceb303cd7b7c59d89e3ced0d3","tid":775232,"uid":31151,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:41:18.000Z","msg":"洗咁多錢緊係想挑戰冠軍架啦 你估好似某d人咁洗極唔夠左賴右賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2784bb6ef5aa0fee4a0b6226b07d96a49aa29287","tid":775232,"uid":55346,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:52:25.000Z","msg":"年年都劍指冠軍嫁啦<br />\n有邊年攞過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a13100a80411d2ce040d66793a6baf91f74c00","tid":775232,"uid":199392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:53:29.000Z","msg":"熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d48fae5107dbe916396c0045f9777fbc6271e7f","tid":775232,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}